<DOCNO>WT16-B24-201</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000254-B017-60</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/FRC/letters/dec96.html 204.71.237.86 19970108124920 text/html 11066
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 12:49:36 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 29-Dec-96 18:50:05 GMT
Content-length: 10879
